OL,6,FMr Hendy, who lived in Severn Beach,
OL,7,Fwas so popular an estimated 700 people
OL,8,Fattended his funeral.
OL,10,FHe has been described as having an
OL,11,F"infectious" personality by his mother
OL,12,FJennifer Hendy. She described his
OL,13,Fsense of humour as "legendary".
OL,15,F"Not a day that goes by where we don't
OL,16,Fthink about Scott," she said.
OL,18,F"He was the kindest, loveliest
OL,19,Fcharacter and all-round amazing son.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
