OL,6,F"His sense of humour was legendary,
OL,7,Fand his loss will be felt from all
OL,8,Fover Bristol such was the reach of his
OL,9,Finfectious personality."
OL,11,FShe described losing her son in such a
OL,12,Fway as "horrendous", saying life will
OL,13,Fnever be the same again.
OL,15,F"We know this would never have
OL,16,Fhappened if Scott wasn't punched," she
OL,17,Fsaid.
