OL,6,F"However, we understand this has
OL,7,Fprobably ruined the offender's life as
OL,8,Fwell; if anything we feel sorry for
OL,9,Fhim and his family. We don't have any
OL,10,Fhatred towards him, we accept he
OL,11,Fprobably didn't mean to kill our son.
OL,13,F"However, we are now left feeling our
OL,14,Fentire life has been torn apart and
OL,15,Fdon't think we will ever come to terms
OL,16,Fwith living our lives without him."
OL,18,FMr Hendy's son Lewis said his father
OL,19,Fwas the heart and soul of their family
OL,20,F- and was idolised by his children.
