OL,6,FHe said: "One of the hardest things to
OL,7,Faccept is that I can no longer reach
OL,8,Fout to Dad. There will be no more
OL,9,Fphone calls to ask for his advice, no
OL,10,Fmore texts to share a quick joke, no
OL,11,Fmore chats about work or life.
OL,13,F"I still pick up the phone to call or
OL,14,Fmessage him, eager to share something
OL,15,Ffunny that's just happened. Then
OL,16,Freality kicks in and I get that
OL,17,Fsinking feeling again because he's no
OL,18,Flonger there.
