OL,6,F"It feels like I've lost my compass,
OL,7,Fmy guide, and the person I could
OL,8,Falways turn to when I needed help."
OL,10,FLewis added: "There are events that
OL,11,Fhave not yet happened that I know will
OL,12,Fbe incredibly bittersweet, such as the
OL,13,Fbirth of my first child and my
OL,14,Fwedding, this also applies to Harvey
OL,15,Fand Holly.
OL,17,F"Dad will never get the opportunity to
OL,18,Fbecome a grandparent, to walk Holly
OL,19,Fdown the aisle and to show us all up
OL,20,Fwith his dance moves at our weddings."
