OL,6,FBaylis, of Redwick Road, was sentenced
OL,7,Fto four years and six months at
OL,8,FBristol Crown Court on Wednesday 29
OL,9,FMay having pleaded guilty to
OL,10,Fmanslaughter in April. He will serve
OL,11,Fat least half of his sentence.
OL,13,FThe court heard there was an
OL,14,Faltercation between the two men in the
OL,15,Fpub car park before Baylis punched Mr
OL,16,FHendy once.
