OL,6,FBaylis was arrested a short distance
OL,7,Faway around 30 minutes after the
OL,8,Fincident. He broke down in front of
OL,9,Fpolice and apologised for what
OL,10,Fhappened, adding he did not want to
OL,11,Fhurt anyone.
OL,13,FDetective Chief Inspector Mark Almond,
OL,14,Fof the Major Crime Investigation Team,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Scott Hendy was clearly a very
OL,16,Fpopular man and our sympathies are
OL,17,Fwith his loved ones at the conclusion
OL,18,Fof these legal proceedings.
