OL,6,F"George Baylis has shown remorse for
OL,7,Fwhat occurred throughout the course of
OL,8,Fenquiries and also pleaded guilty
OL,9,Fearly on to manslaughter.
OL,11,F"While there is no evidence of any
OL,12,Fintent on his part to cause the fatal
OL,13,Finjuries he did, this case highlights
OL,14,Fthe tragic reality that one punch can
OL,15,Fkill. In that split second, he lashed
OL,16,Fout he unintentionally took Scott's
OL,17,Flife and now has received a lengthy
OL,18,Fprison sentence."
